    "statement": {
      "informal": "Multiplication on the positive reals is a single F16 node: F16fn(x, y) = exp(log(x) + log(y)) = x · y for x, y > 0. The headline 'mul_pos = 1n' result that drops the SuperBEST positive-domain headline from 16n to 14n.",
